        "meta_description": "While I've seen plenty of good folks tell others in threads about this, it is clearly not reaching people well enough. Link to the thread about it on official forums: http://www.shadowrun.com/forums/discussion/28437/berlin-is-more-like-genesis-game-more-open-world/p1 Seattle is more of a personal introduction to the game/world. Linear due to being focused on one, straight narrative. Berlin is more traditional Mercenary Shadowrun.",
